      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/eng-asv/PSA074.htm",
      "text": "Oh deliver not the soul of thy turtle-dove unto the wild beast: Forget not the life of thy poor for ever.",
      "versionTitle": "American Standard Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 74:19",
